  <sect><heading>IP pool commands<label id="ippool"></heading>

<p>
Mpd implementing dynamic IP addresses pool management. When user
is authenticated and auth backend have not provided IP address,
it can be taken from pool. To make work it you should create
one or more address pools with 'set ippool add ...'
commands and define which pool should be used for the link
using 'set auth ippool ...' command.

<descrip>

<tag><tt>
set ippool add <em>pool</em> <em>first</em> <em>last</em>
</tt></tag>

This command creates new IP address pool if it not exists and adds specified 
address range to it.

</descrip>

</p>
